		<h2>List of contributions</h2>
		<ul>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2014/index.html">SLE 2014</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2014/paper03.html">Towards User-Friendly Projectional Editors</a></em> (<a href="../profile/MarkusVölter.html">Markus Völter</a>, <a href="../profile/JanetSiegmund.html">Janet Siegmund</a>, <a href="../profile/ThorstenBerger.html"><span class="info">Thorsten Berger</span></a>, <a href="../profile/BerndKolb.html">Bernd Kolb</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2016/index.html">SLE 2016</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2016/paper03.html">Efficient Development of Consistent Projectional Editors using Grammar Cells</a></em> (<a href="../profile/MarkusVölter.html">Markus Völter</a>, <a href="../profile/TamásSzabó.html">Tamás Szabó</a>, <a href="../profile/SaschaLisson.html">Sascha Lisson</a>, <a href="../profile/BerndKolb.html">Bernd Kolb</a>, <a href="../profile/SebastianErdweg.html">Sebastian Erdweg</a>, <a href="../profile/ThorstenBerger.html"><span class="info">Thorsten Berger</span></a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2017/index.html">SLE 2017</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2017/paper07.html">A chrestomathy of DSL implementations</a></em> (<a href="../profile/SimonSchauss.html">Simon Schauss</a>, <a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html">Ralf Lämmel</a>, <a href="../profile/JohannesHärtel.html">Johannes Härtel</a>, <a href="../profile/MarcelHeinz.html">Marcel Heinz</a>, <a href="../profile/KevinKlein.html">Kevin Klein</a>, <a href="../profile/LukasHärtel.html">Lukas Härtel</a>, <a href="../profile/ThorstenBerger.html"><span class="info">Thorsten Berger</span></a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2019/index.html">SLE 2019</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2019/paper13.html">High-level mission specification for multiple robots</a></em> (<a href="../profile/SergioGarcía.html">Sergio García</a>, <a href="../profile/PatrizioPelliccione.html">Patrizio Pelliccione</a>, <a href="../profile/ClaudioMenghi.html">Claudio Menghi</a>, <a href="../profile/ThorstenBerger.html"><span class="info">Thorsten Berger</span></a>, <a href="../profile/TomášBureš.html">Tomáš Bureš</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2020/index.html">SLE 2020</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2020/paper08.html">Behavior Trees in Action: A Study of Robotics Applications</a></em> (<a href="../profile/RazanGhzouli.html">Razan Ghzouli</a>, <a href="../profile/ThorstenBerger.html"><span class="info">Thorsten Berger</span></a>, <a href="../profile/EinarBrochJohnsen.html">Einar Broch Johnsen</a>, <a href="../profile/SwaibDragule.html">Swaib Dragule</a>, <a href="../profile/AndrzejWąsowski.html">Andrzej Wąsowski</a>) </li>
